Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Add labels to plot elements", "Subsubsection",ExpressionUUID->"473a1f75-9e53-4b1e-a487-b7928be0591e"],

Cell["\<\
Data is meaningless without a reference point, whether that reference is a \
label, scale or value. This module demonstrates how to add labeling, such as:\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"d9f8225e-e654-4938-b66e-7c4985ab8273"],

